tch analysis\\n    - Interview summary\\n    - Technical assessment\\n    - Behavioral assessment\\n    - Strengths and weaknesses\\n    - Final recommendation and scoring breakdown\\n\\nFinal output: Evaluation report of candidate in .txt\\n\\n---\\n# **Context from Upstream Tasks**\\nNo completed previous tasks context available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task2:\\n  Objective: Develop resume–job match analysis algorithm to produce match scores and key alignment points\\nTask task3:\\n  Objective: Implement AI-based dynamic interview engine that generates technical and behavioral questions and follow-ups\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nParse and structure candidate resume into a profile data model\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nJSON\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"candidate_profile\\\": {\\n    \\\"personal_information\\\": {\\n      \\\"name\\\": null,\\n      \\\"email\\\": null,\\n      \\\"phone\\\": null,\\n      \\\"linkedin\\\": null,\\n      \\\"location\\\": null\\n    },\\n    \\\"summary\\\": null,\\n    \\\"skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"experience\\\": [\\n      {\\n        \\\"title\\\": null,\\n        \\\"company\\\": null,\\n        \\\"location\\\": null,\\n        \\\"dates\\\": {\\n          \\\"start_date\\\": null,\\n          \\\"end_date\\\": null\\n        },\\n        \\\"description\\\": null,\\n        \\\"responsibilities\\\": []\\n      }\\n    ],\\n    \\\"education\\\": [\\n      {\\n        \\\"degree\\\": null,\\n        \\\"university\\\": null,\\n        \\\"location\\\": null,\\n        \\\"dates\\\": {\\n          \\\"start_date\\\": null,\\n          \\\"end_date\\\": null\\n        },\\n        \\\"description\\\": null,\\n        \\\"major\\\": null\\n      }\\n    ],\\n    \\\"projects\\\": [\\n      {\\n        \\\"name\\\": null,\\n        \\\"description\\\": null,\\n        \\\"technologies\\\": [],\\n        \\\"url\\\": null,\\n        \\\"dates