{"timestamp": "2026-05-26 16:02:31,950", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.validation", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_gpt_conversation", "line": 403, "message": "{\n  \"event_type\": \"gpt_conversation\",\n  \"task_id\": \"task_2\",\n  \"conversation_type\": \"task_execution\",\n  \"iteration\": 1,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"\\n# Role:\\nHelp me produce a precise and detailed solution for the given task. Follow these instructions exactly:\\n\\n# Objective & Steps:\\n1. Ensure Completeness:\\n   - Avoid placeholders or incomplete text.\\n   - Your output must meet all requirements of the task.\\n   - Include all necessary details so that the output is self-contained and can be directly used as input for downstream tasks.\\n\\n2. Maintain Precision and Clarity:\\n   - Your output will be used as input for subsequent tasks; therefore, it must be comprehensive and precise.\\n   - **Output the answer only without any jusifications**\\n\\n3. Avoid Repetition:\\n   - Do not repeat verbatim any content from previous tasks.\\n   - Ensure your output is original and adds value to the workflow.\\n\\n\\n\\n# Audience:\\nYour output will be used as a solution for the given task, it will be used in the later validation and intergration process.\\n\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"# **The Overall Goal**\\nPerform interview and candidate evaluation  for a candidate.\\n\\nyou should:\\n- Analyze job descriptions and candidate resumes\\n- Conduct dynamic AI-based interviews with technical and behavioral questions\\n- Generate follow-up questions based on candidate responses\\n- Evaluate candidate answers for relevance, depth, confidence, and technical accuracy\\n- Score candidates across multiple evaluation categories\\n- Generate recruiter communication emails such as interview invitations and follow-ups\\n- Produce a final candidate evaluation report containing:\\n    - Resume-job match analysis\\n    - Interview summary\\n    - Technical assessment\\n    - Behavioral assessment\\n    - Strengths and weaknesses\\n    - Final recommendation and scoring breakdown\\n\\nFinal output: Evaluation report of candidate in .txt\\n\\n---\\n# **Context from Upstream Tasks**\\nNo completed previous tasks context available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nNo downstream objectives available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nDevelop email template generator for interview invitations and follow-up communications\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPython code\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```python\\ndef generate_interview_invitation_email(candidate_name, job_title, interview_date, interview_time, interview_location, interviewer_name, interviewer_title, contact_email, additional_instructions=None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates an email invitation for an interview.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        candidate_name (str): The name of the candidate.\\n        job_title (str): The title of the job the candidate is interviewing for.\\n        interview_date (str): The date of the interview (e.g., \\\"October 26, 2023\\\").\\n        interview_time (str): The time of the interview (e.g., \\\"10:00 AM - 11:00 AM\\\").\\n        interview_location (str): The location of the interview (e.g., \\\"Zoom Meeting - Link: [Zoom Link]\\\" or \\\"123 Main Street, Anytown, USA\\\").\\n        interviewer_name (str): The name of the interviewer.\\n        interviewer_title (str): The title of the interviewer.\\n        contact_email (str):  The email address for the candidate to contact with questions.\\n        additional_instructions (str, optional): Any additional instructions for the candidate. Defaults to None.\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: The complete email message.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    subject = f\\\"Interview Invitation: {job_title} at [Company Name]\\\" # Replace [Company Name]\\n    body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"Dear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for your interest in the {job_title} position at [Company Name].\\n\\nWe are pleased to invite you to an interview to further discuss your qualifications.\\n\\nHere are the details of your interview:\\n\\n*   **Date:** {interview_date}\\n*   **Time:** {interview_time}\\n*   **Location:** {interview_location}\\n\\nYou will be interviewing with {interviewer_name}, {interviewer_title}.\\n\\nPlease come prepared to discuss your experience and skills related to the {job_title} position.\\n\\n{f'Additional Instructions: {additional_instructions}\\\\n\\\\n' if additional_instructions else ''}\\n\\nIf you have any questions or need to reschedule, please do not hesitate to contact us at {contact_email}.\\n\\nWe look forward to meeting you!\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n\\\"\\\"\\\" # Replace [Company Name], [Your Name], [Your Title]\\n    return f\\\"Subject: {subject}\\\\n\\\\n{body}\\\"\\n\\n\\ndef generate_interview_followup_email(candidate_name, job_title, interviewer_name, contact_email, feedback_deadline=None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates a follow-up email to a candidate after an interview.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        candidate_name (str): The name of the candidate.\\n        job_title (str): The title of the job the candidate interviewed for.\\n        interviewer_name (str): The name of the interviewer.\\n        contact_email (str):  The email address for the candidate to contact with questions.\\n        feedback_deadline (str, optional): The deadline by which the candidate should expect feedback. Defaults to None.\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: The complete email message.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    subject = f\\\"Following Up: {job_title} Interview at [Company Name]\\\" # Replace [Company Name]\\n    body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"Dear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for taking the time to interview with {interviewer_name} for the {job_title} position at [Company Name]. We appreciate you sharing your experience and qualifications with us.\\n\\nWe are currently reviewing all applications and will be in touch with an update on the status of your application.\\n\\n{f'You can expect to hear from us by {feedback_deadline}.\\\\n\\\\n' if feedback_deadline else ''}\\n\\nIn the meantime, if you have any questions, please feel free to contact us at {contact_email}.\\n\\nThank you again for your interest in [Company Name].\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n\\\"\\\"\\\" # Replace [Company Name], [Your Name], [Your Title]\\n    return f\\\"Subject: {subject}\\\\n\\\\n{body}\\\"\\n\\n\\nif __name__ == '__main__':\\n    # Example Usage: Invitation Email\\n    invitation_email = generate_interview_invitation_email(\\n        candidate_name=\\\"Jane Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        interview_date=\\\"November 2, 2023\\\",\\n        interview_time=\\\"2:00 PM - 3:00 PM\\\",\\n        interview_location=\\\"Zoom Meeting - Link: [Zoom Meeting Link]\\\",\\n        interviewer_name=\\\"John Smith\\\",\\n        interviewer_title=\\\"Engineering Manager\\\",\\n        contact_email=\\\"recruiting@example.com\\\",\\n        additional_instructions=\\\"Please bring a copy of your portfolio.\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"--- Interview Invitation Email ---\\\")\\n    print(invitation_email)\\n\\n    # Example Usage: Follow-up Email\\n    followup_email = generate_interview_followup_email(\\n        candidate_name=\\\"Jane Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        interviewer_name=\\\"John Smith\\\",\\n        contact_email=\\\"recruiting@example.com\\\",\\n        feedback_deadline=\\\"November 9, 2023\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"\\\\n--- Interview Follow-up Email ---\\\")\\n    print(followup_email)\\n```\\n\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-26T16:02:31.950717\"\n}"}
