    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"location\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"summary\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"experience\\\": [],\\n    \\\"education\\\": [],\\n    \\\"projects\\\": [],\\n    \\\"certifications\\\": [],\\n    \\\"awards\\\": [],\\n    \\\"volunteer_experience\\\": [],\\n    \\\"publications\\\": [],\\n    \\\"languages\\\": [],\\n    \\\"interests\\\": [],\\n    \\\"references\\\": []\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task3:\\n  Objective: Implement AI-based dynamic interview engine that generates technical and behavioral questions and follow-ups\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nDevelop email template generator for interview invitations and follow-up communications\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPython code\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```python\\ndef generate_interview_invitation_email(candidate_name, interview_date, interview_time, interviewer_name, meeting_link, job_title, company_name):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates an email invitation for an interview.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        candidate_name (str): The name of the candidate.\\n        interview_date (str): The date of the interview (e.g., \\\"October 26, 2023\\\").\\n        interview_time (str): The time of the interview (e.g., \\\"10:00 AM PST\\\").\\n        interviewer_name (str): The name of the interviewer.\\n        meeting_link (str): The link to the online meeting.\\n        job_title (str): The title of the job the candidate is interviewing for.\\n        company_name (str): The name of the company.\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: The generated email invitation.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    subject = f\\\"Interview Invitation: {job_title} at {company_name}\\\"\\n    body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nWe are pleased to invite you to interview for the {job_title} position at {company_name}.\\n\\nYour interview is scheduled for:\\n\\nDate: {interview_date}\\nTime: {interview_time}\\nInterviewer: {interviewer_name}\\nMeeting Link: {meeting_link}\\n\\nPlease join the meeting at the scheduled time by clicking on the link above.\\n\\nWe look forward to speaking with you!\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\nThe {company_name} Recruiting Team\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    return subject, body\\n\\n\\ndef generate_interview_followup_email(candidate_name, interviewer_name, job_title, company_name):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates a follow-up email after an interview.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        candidate_name (str): The name of the candidate.\\n        interviewer_name (str): The name of the interviewer.\\n        job_title (str): The title of the job the candidate interviewed for.\\n        company_name (str): The name of the company.\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: The generated follow-up email.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    subject = f\\\"Thank you for interviewing with {company_name}\\\"\\n    body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for taking the time to interview with {interviewer_name} for the {job_title} position at {company_name}.\\n\\nWe appreciate you sharing your experience and qualifications with us.\\n\\nWe are currently reviewing all candidates and will be in touch with you regarding the next steps in the hiring process.\\n\\nThank you again for your interest in {company_name}.\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\nThe {company_name} Recruiting Team\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    return subject, body\\n\\n\\ndef generate_rejection_email(candidate_name, job_title, company_name):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates a rejection email after an interview.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        candidate_name (str): The name of the candidate.\\n        job_title (str): The title of the job the candidate interviewed for.\\n        company_name (str): The name of the company.\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: The generated rejection email.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    subject = f\\\"Update on your application for {job_title} at {company_name}\\\"\\n    body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for your interest in the {job_title} position at {company_name}. We appreciate you taking the time to interview with our team.\\n\\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose qualifications and experience more closely align with the requirements of this role.\\n\\nThis was a difficult decision, as we were impressed with many aspects of your background. We encourage you to apply for other positions at {company_name} that may be a good fit for your skills and experience.\\n\\nWe wish you the best of luck in your job search.\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\nThe {company_name} Recruiting Team\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    return subject, body\\n\\n\\ndef generate_offer_email(candidate_name, job_title, company_name, salary, start_date, benefits_summary):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates an offer email for a candidate.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        candidate_name (str): The name of the candidate.\\n        job_title (str): The title of the job being offered.\\n        company_name (str): The name of the company.\\n        salary (str): The salary being offered (e.g., \\\"$100,000 per year\\\").\\n        start_date (str): The start date of the job (e.g., \\\"November 1, 2023\\\").\\n        benefits_summary (str): A brief summary of the benefits offered.\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: The generated offer email.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    subject = f\\\"Job Offer: {job_title} at {company_name}\\\"\\n    body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nWe are delighted to offer you the position of {job_title} at {company_name}!\\n\\nWe were very impressed with your qualifications and experience during the interview process, and we believe you would be a valuable asset to our team.\\n\\nHere are the details of our offer:\\n\\nJob Title: {job_title}\\nSalary: {salary}\\nStart Date: {start_date}\\nBenefits: {benefits_summary}\\n\\nWe have attached a formal offer letter with more details about the position and benefits. Please review it carefully and let us know if you have any questions.\\n\\nWe are excited about the possibility of you joining our team! Please let us know your decision by [Date].\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\nThe {company_name} Recruiting Team\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    return subject, body\\n```\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-26T16:03:21.634556\"\n}"}
